Instrument Number: 20210104001948 Document:L Rec: $104
Record Date: 1/4/2021 4:15 PM King County, WA
Recording No. 20040204000499, that Community Fiber Networks, LLC has a lien claim against
Grantors above and the above described property in Issaquah, WA for unpaid HFN services
for the period of January 1, 2019 through December 30. 2020 in the amount of $1359.00. In
addition. the Grantee hereunder has a claim for any additional services, fees, and interest
which accrue after December 30, 2020 and for attorney's fees and costs associated with the
filing of this lien and collection of the fees and sums described herein.
Notice of Claim of Lien - page 2
Anyone acquiring an interest in said property is on notice of the Claim of Lien set forth herein.
Current payoff information regarding the claim and this lien may be obtained from the
undersigned.
Dated this ___ day of January. 2021.
ISOMEDIA, INC ., Authorized Agent for
Community Fiber Networks, LLC.
P.O. Box 58288
Seattle. WA 98138
Phone 425-427-0999; 425-605-5700
By:
President

I am reliably informed that ISOMEDIA, INC. is the authorized representative for Community

Fiber Networks, LLC, a Washington limited liability company, and that Bruce Straughan is the
President of ISOMEDIA, INC. who appeared before me, and acknowledged that he signed this
instrument on behalf of ISOMEDIA, INC. acting as the authorized agent of Community Fiber
Networks, LLC. on oath stated that he was authorized to execute this instrument and
acknowledged it as the free and voluntary act of the Grantor named above for the uses and
purposes mentioned in this instrument.
